name: life
description:
Human beings are a life form that can create bridges over rivers, lakes, seas, spaces, all the way to the other side of the water, or any matter, or non-matter. 

First the waters. The air. The moon. 

Soon through spacetime to Mars. Further Beyond. 

Human beings think and create to bridge themselves with other places, and to carry their lives and life to a new land & new time. 

In which space ship or planet will this work be looked at in the future? By whom? By ai or human beings, or both?

Original art by tomi with ai on 2021-10-16. 

3584 × 6400px
